This paper is about image attribute transfer, which is a topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method uses a GAN architecture, which is a popular deep learning technique in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the use of latent variables, which is a common technique in generative models and optimization (cs.GR). Finally, the paper evaluates its method on popular image datasets, which is a common practice in multimedia (cs.MM).
